<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4747127>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Male of Leptostylum leuconotum (Wulp, 1892), deposited at MZSP. From Serra da Cantareira, São Paulo, Brazil. (a) Head, dorsal view. (b) Head, frontal view. (c) Head, lateral view. (d) Dorsal habitus. (e) Lateral habitus. (f) Wing, dorsal view. (g) Abdomen, latero-ventral view, showing sex patch on tergite 4. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4747127/files/figure.png" .

